high_descs: Turn right and go to the front of the sink.
Pick up the gray knife on the right on the edge of the counter.
Move over right to the counter top with the apple
Cut the apple into three parts.
Move back left to the sink.
Place the gray knife in the sink.
Move right back to the counter with the cut apple.
Pick up one piece of the apple.
Go to the front of the microwave on the top of the counter on the right.
Remove the apple piece from the microwave after heating it.
Turn left to go back to the sink.
Place the apple piece in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated piece of apple in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and step forward to face the sink.
Pick up the knife on the edge of the sink.
Look to the right to face the apple on the counter.
Cut the apple on the counter into three pieces.
Look to the left to face the sink.
Place the knife in the sink.
Look to the right to face the apple on the counter.
Pick up a piece of apple on the counter.
Turn right to face the microwave.
Heat the apple in the microwave and remove it.
Turn left to face the sink.
Place the apple in the sink.
anns.task_desc: To heat an apple and place it in the sink.

high_descs: Go straight, turn right. Walk to the sink.
Pick up the knife near the sink.
Turn left, turn left, turn left, turn left to the microwave.
Cut the apple into slices.
Turn left, turn right, walk straight to the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Turn left, turn left, turn left, turn left to the microwave.
Pick up the slice of fruit.
Turn left, walk straight, turn right to the microwave.
Open the microwave. Put the apple inside. Turn on the microwave. Close the microwave.
Open the microwave. Take the apple. Turn left to the sink.
Put the apple into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked apple slice into the sink.
